snippet.title: Advent NEON - Official Developer Video | Black Voices in Gaming 2024
snippet.description: Meet CryoGX and learn about this solo developer working on Advent Neon. Advent Neon is a hyperactive 2D action platformer with wicked fast attacks, omnidirectional dashing, and time-freezing! Play well enough to transform and unleash 100% power!
